et remanded."],[2615,2740,"Do you really wanna see"],[2740,3007,"your mom rot behind jail bars?"],[4208,4270,"Mom,"],[4337,4500,"how am I gonna get you out now?"],[5342,5438,"I have to admit,"],[5438,5488,"you're not just"],[5488,5655,"a one-night kind of gal."],[5747,5855,"I know"],[5855,5968,"asking Mr. Larsen"],[5968,6085,"would be a mistake, but"],[6122,6210,"he's the only one"],[6210,6339,"that can save my mom now."]],"7":[[325,421,"I figured we would see"],[421,496,"each other again."],[571,717,"Just didn't think it'd be this soon."],[759,846,"Mr. Larsen,"],[971,1051,"I'm in trouble."],[1126,1205,"I need your help."],[1280,1368,"What kind of trouble?"],[1451,1668,"I need a million dollars."],[1764,1835,"Can you help me?"],[1972,2060,"Boy, you don't waste time"],[2060,2156,"with words, do you?"],[2239,2385,"But I'm a businessman,"],[2460,2585,"and we deal with trades."],[4654,4725,"Yesterday"],[4808,4884,"at the hotel,"],[4884,4988,"you seemed interested."],[4988,5071,"So I thought-"],[5376,5459,"You thought what?"],[5780,5864,"That you wanted me."],[5972,6026,"I'm clean."],[6026,6143,"I've never been with anyone,"],[6143,6252,"so you don't have to worry."],[6485,6581,"So you came here"],[6581,6748,"to sell your body for a check?"],[6831,6931,"They send me women"],[6931,7052,"like party favors."],[7119,7203,"Models,"],[7273,7390,"pageant queens,"],[7457,7549,"actresses,"],[7611,7703,"even royalty."],[7907,8012,"So Miss Nola Carter,"],[8012,8162,"why should I pay for sex?"],[8229,8345,"How do you know my name?"],[8400,8487,"Did you look me up?"],[8512,8583,"In my position,"],[8583,8808,"only one phone call is all it takes."],[9509,9580,"Chris Wilton,"],[9642,9722,"your boyfriend"],[9743,9897,"and my daughter's fiancé."],[10043,10181,"Miss Nola Carter, what is this?"],[10360,10422,"A setup?"]],"8":[[58,129,"No."],[229,304,"Mr. Larsen,"],[304,437,"I ran into you by accident."],[446,513,"We were already-"],[513,700,"I don't care about your drama, kiddo."],[713,792,