oing here?"],[508,583,"Sam told me"],[583,700,"you got in trouble at school."],[750,859,"I was already on my way,"],[859,955,"but it looks like your mother"],[955,1026,"beat me to it."],[1138,1267,"Nola, what happened here?"],[1351,1601,"He said my name for the first time."],[1697,1851,"Well, they're saying"],[1851,2010,"that Lucas started a fight"],[2010,2118,"with this young man,"],[2198,2302,"and because his parents"],[2302,2444,"are of higher status,"],[2444,2573,"Lucas should be expelled."],[2902,3015,"It was my son's fault."],[3036,3115,"No it wasn't!"],[3174,3294,"Lucas is a good kid."],[3315,3486,"I don't believe for one second"],[3499,3611,"he would pick a fight."],[3616,3666,"Yes."],[3666,3795,"Yes, of course."],[3828,4087,"My son was too rowdy."],[4087,4245,"It was not Lucas' fault."],[4262,4295,"Really?"],[4295,4404,"Because just a minute ago,"],[4404,4525,"you were saying how Lucas"],[4525,4654,"was gonna end up in juvie,"],[4696,4817,"and you threw hot tea at him."],[4817,4950,"I think you owe him an apology."],[5109,5221,"Yes, yes."],[5271,5351,"Of course."],[5434,5593,"I'm sorry, Lucas."],[5834,5880,"Tim,"],[6001,6181,"fire her husband immediately"],[6181,6377,"and strip him off the board permanently."],[6489,6606,"I'll be filing charges"],[6606,6715,"for what she just did."],[6886,6956,"And you,"],[7069,7178,"as the faculty member,"],[7178,7328,"you failed to protect your students."],[7328,7449,"You're out of here as well."],[7570,7682,"Please, Mr. Larsen,"],[7682,7820,"give me one more chance, please!"],[7832,7995,"Please, Mr. Larsen, please!"],[7999,8128,"I beg you, please!"],[8149,8274,"Mr. Larsen!"],[8787,8846,"Come here."]],"47":[[104,166,"Dad,"],[308,408,"I'm sorry."],[496,617,"Toby said,"],[717,992,"I don't have a mom or a dad,"],[992,1401,"and I'm a kid nobody wanted."],[1493,1584,"He said that to you?"],[1668,1872,"I pushed him because of that."],[1939,2139,"I didn't mean to."],[2193,2256,"Hey,"],[2310,2364,"listen."],[2460,2573,"You're not